OL,3,CClassroom closures at four schools
OL,4,Cafter ceiling collapse
OL,6,FFour schools on North Tyneside have
OL,7,Fbeen forced to close or partially
OL,8,Fclose due to construction issues.
OL,10,FHundreds of children's education will
OL,11,Fbe disrupted as a result.
OL,13,FThe issues came to light after a
OL,14,Fceiling at Fordley Primary School, in
OL,15,FAnnitsford, collapsed late last year
OL,16,Fwhen a chunk of concrete fell through
OL,17,Fit.
OL,19,FNo one was injured in the incident,
OL,20,Fwhich happened overnight.
