OL,6,FIt led to check whether other schools
OL,7,Fhad undergone similar construction
OL,8,Fmethods, which resulted in the closure
OL,9,For partial closure of Hazelwood
OL,10,FPrimary School, Churchill Community
OL,11,FCollege and Grasmere Academy.
