OL,6,FNorth Tyneside Council thanked
OL,7,Ffamilies and children for their
OL,8,Fpatience while investigations are
OL,9,Fcarried out.
OL,11,FJon Ritchie, director of resources at
OL,12,FNorth Tyneside Council, told ITV Tyne
OL,13,FTees: "It's important to balance the
OL,14,Fhealth and safety of our pupils and
OL,15,Fstaff with the disruption for
OL,16,Ffamilies, but also for their
OL,17,Feducation. I'm massively sympathetic
OL,18,Fwith parents for the short notice.
