OL,6,F"We're looking at working with the
OL,7,Fschools to support them in the short
OL,8,Fterm and the longer term."
OL,10,FIn a statement, he added: "I'd like to
OL,11,Freassure everyone that these
OL,12,Fstructural issues are not related to
OL,13,FRAAC and we are working alongside the
OL,14,FDepartment for Education's complex
OL,15,Fprojects team to find solutions."
