OL,6,FMP Catherine McKinnell, a shadow
OL,7,Feducation minister, said: "The
OL,8,Fgovernment needs to get a plan in
OL,9,Fplace for how they're going to address
OL,10,Fnot just RAAC - we're still waiting on
OL,11,Fthat - but now other structural issues
OL,12,Fthat we know are appearing in
OL,13,Fbuildings in so many places and now
OL,14,Fhere on North Tyneside.
OL,16,F"It's incredibly frustrating for the
OL,17,Fchildren affected, for the parents and
OL,18,Ffor the teachers."
